now people have twisted it and made it, "Aiyyo,

63
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:21,580
karma."

64
00:04:21,580 --> 00:04:24,840
Karma is not something that you inherit, kand...
ma...

65
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:27,700
karma is in what you're doing right now.

66
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:37,229
So, what life throws at you is not always
your choice, but what you do with it or how

67
00:04:37,229 --> 00:04:39,300
you hit it is your choice.

68
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:47,610
Right now, there is a corner, that is the
way it is, but how you take the corner is

69
00:04:47,610 --> 00:04:49,630
entirely yours.

70
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:51,720
Let's say somebody goes and crashes in this
corner.

71
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:54,479
Now, they say, "The corner was difficult."

72
00:04:54,479 --> 00:04:55,479
That's not the point.

73
00:04:55,479 --> 00:04:58,140
You didn't know how to take it, that's all
it is.

74
00:04:58,140 --> 00:04:59,970
That's so with every aspect of life.

75
00:04:59,970 --> 00:05:03,940
That's what karma means, it's your doing.

76
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:08,300
If you make it, it's you; if you don't make
it, it's you.

77
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:12,979
This is the only culture which has looked
at life like this.

78
00:05:12,979 --> 00:05:15,009
Everywhere they're saying, "God - he is doing
everything."

79
00:05:15,009 --> 00:05:23,130
