fertilizer, but no organic content.

118
00:07:49,889 --> 00:07:55,830
Why organic content is, this whole process
of life happens because of microbial activity.

119
00:07:55,830 --> 00:08:00,010
Even you, you're a bodybuilder, but sixty
percent, hmm?

120
00:08:00,010 --> 00:08:02,770
